      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 997.1 Carrera S featuring the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a precision 6-speed manual transaxle. This example is mechanically superior, having received an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a documented borescope inspection confirming zero cylinder scoring. The chassis is dialed in with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber on lightweight staggered alloys. Performance is enhanced by a center-muffler delete for a more resonant exhaust note without compromising backpressure. The paint retains a deep luster with zero swirl marks, and the interior demonstrates negligible bolster wear, reflecting its pampered history. A truly turn-key, analog masterpiece for the serious collector.",
